                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1674-18430508 t18430508-1674-punishment-244"></join>To enter into his own recognizances of 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. to keep the peace for two years.</rs>
               </p>
